1. This was part of the whole federal

01:28.869 --> 01:37.098
concept of regional fair share in housing. Yeah. 
They called it the Regional Housing Mobility

01:37.378 --> 01:40.481
Program. And those were the old days of the area 
wide housing opportunity plans where you would

01:40.862 --> 01:48.970
tell a community how many units they were going to 
take and so forth. Yeah, it was an attempt to

01:48.990 --> 01:51.493
homogenize the entire region. Or an attempt to get 
